						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in front of the Rāmaliṅgasvāmin temple.</p>						

						<p>1441 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1363, Raudri, Pushya ba. 30, Sunday <hi rend="italic">ardhōdaya</hi> corresponding to 1441 A.D. January 23, Monday f.d.t. °09. There was a solar eclipse on this day, which was however, not mentioned in the record.</p>						

						<p>It registers the gift of land of 3 <hi rend="italic">kha</hi> in extent situated at Cheṁnnapalli to the God Velūpūru Rāmayadēva by Velupuri Kēśaojjulu for the merit of himself and his parents.</p>						

						</summary>
